266
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:10,315
Well, I do.

267
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:12,476
I got thousands of dollars in my pocket.

268
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:15,870
I'm gonna reach into my back pocket
