It's against my religion.

276
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:11,553
- Great.
- I'm a Buddhist.

277
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:13,596
Yeah. You're a Kung Fu priest.

278
00:19:16,560 --> 00:19:17,959
