285
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,709
He knows 'em.

286
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:48,190
I'm tellin' you, Captain, this guy is weird.

287
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:49,633
Yeah, show me a cop who isn't.

288
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:52,280
