367
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:11,435
And we have bigger fish to fry.

368
00:27:12,080 --> 00:27:13,433
Whatever you say.

369
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:23,549
"Ten Ways To Spend Your Weekend."

